Anouar H. Smaine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anouar_H._Smaine 0 Anouar H. Smaine (born 1976) is an American film director, producer, actor, and screenwriter of Algerian descent. He is the son of a French professor, and an actor and playwright. Anouar_H._Smaine ( born 1976 ) is an_American_film_director , producer , actor , and screenwriter of Algerian_descent .
